ties":{"id":"20230305205650-rwm6qon","updated":"20230305205650"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"转义字符:以反斜杠\"\"开头，后跟一个或几个字符、如'\\n', t'等，分别代表换行、横向跳格.'表示的是\\‘%%’‘\\’","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205651-wtz7mot","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205651-wtz7mot","updated":"20230305205651"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"字符变量:"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用char定义，每个字符变量被分配一个字节的内存空间字符值以ASCII码的形式存放在变量的内存单元中;","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205652-2d3a31e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205652-2d3a31e","updated":"20230305205652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注:char a;","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205653-v0wl0ec","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205653-v0wl0ec","updated":"20230305205653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"a = 'x';","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205654-fwexpub","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205654-fwexpub","updated":"20230305205654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"a变量中存放的是字符'x'的ASCll:120即a=120跟a='x'在本质上是一致的.","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205655-ilar2mn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205655-ilar2mn","updated":"20230305205655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"字符串常量","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205656-7b8lo3b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205656-7b8lo3b","updated":"20230305205656"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是由双引号括起来的字符序列，如“CHINA”、“哈哈哈”\"C program”，“$12.5\"等都是合法的字符串常量.","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205657-ldojtpa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205657-ldojtpa","updated":"20230305205657"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"字符串常量与字符常​量的不同"}]},{"ID":"20230305205658-1tmmks7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205658-1tmmks7","updated":"20230305205658"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"'a'为字符常量，\"a\"为字符串常量每个字符串的结尾，编译器会自动的添加一个结束标志位'\\O'，即“a”包含两个字符'a'和'\\O'","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205659-7u2od13","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205659-7u2od13","updated":"20230305205659"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关键字","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205660-vi2djix","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205660-vi2djix","updated":"20230305205660"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"存储相关关键字","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205661-x5nk9dr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205661-x5nk9dr","updated":"20230305205661"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、register","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205662-u6fscdl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205662-u6fscdl","updated":"20230305205662"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是寄存器的意思，用register修饰的变量是寄存器变量，","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205663-8t1sx98","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205663-8t1sx98","updated":"20230305205663"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"即︰在编译的时候告诉编译器这个变量是寄存器变量，尽量将其存储空间分配在寄存器中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205664-zlmabct","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205664-zlmabct","updated":"20230305205664"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205665-5uzyjuh","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20230305205665-5uzyjuh","updated":"20230305205665"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20230305205666-rq5l4mm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205666-rq5l4mm","updated":"20230305205666"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(1)∶定义的变量不一定真的存放在寄存器中。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(2): cpu取数据的时候去寄存器中拿数据比去内存中拿数据要快(3)︰因为寄存器比较宝贵，所以不能定义寄存器数组","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(4) : register只能修饰字符型及整型的，不能修饰浮点型","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(5)∶因为register修饰的变量可能存放在寄存器中不存放在内存中，所以不能对寄存器变量取地址。因为只有存放在内存中的数据才有地址","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20230305205667-urjsnxy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205667-urjsnxy","updated":"20230305205667"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、static","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205668-krapvca","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205668-krapvca","updated":"20230305205668"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是静态的意思","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205669-y9l7uy7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205669-y9l7uy7","updated":"20230305205669"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"static可以修饰全局变量、局部变量、函数","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用static修饰的变量，此变量保存在内存的静态区空间中","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205670-rqx0ipm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205670-rqx0ipm","updated":"20230305205670"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、const","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205671-lgabgi0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205671-lgabgi0","updated":"20230305205671"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"const是常量的意思","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用const修饰的变量是只读的，不能修改它的值","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"const int a=101;//在定义a的时候用const修饰，并赋初值为101从此以后，就不能再给a赋值了","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"a=111;//错误的","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205672-eide6yn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205672-eide6yn","updated":"20230305205672"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4、auto","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205673-e6p8w7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205673-e6p8w7d","updated":"20230305205673"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"auto int a和int a是等价的，auto关键字现在基本不用","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205674-jitegeu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205674-jitegeu","updated":"20230305205674"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5、extern","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205675-ehzrrof","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205675-ehzrrof","updated":"20230305205675"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是外部的意思，一般用于函数和全局变量的声明","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205676-7up3de5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205676-7up3de5","updated":"20230305205676"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"控制语句相关关键字","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205677-f5hju18","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205677-f5hju18","updated":"20230305205677"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"条件控制语句:","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"202