e":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205686-k7d93dv","updated":"20230305205686"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用来测变量、数组的占用存储空间的大小(字节数)","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205687-gn2q4xz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205687-gn2q4xz","updated":"20230305205687"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"typedef","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205688-owyux0p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205688-owyux0p","updated":"20230305205688"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重命名相关的关键字","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关键字，作用是给一个已有的类型，重新起个类型名，并没有创造一个新的类型","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205689-8vqdhv0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205689-8vqdhv0","updated":"20230305205689"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、用想起名的类型定义一个变量 short int a;","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、用新的类型名替代变量名 short int INT16;","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、在最前面加typedef short int lNT16;","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4、就可以用新的类型名定义变量了INT16 b和short int b是一个效果","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205690-lam0hnx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205690-lam0hnx","updated":"20230305205690"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"volatile","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205691-7r06r50","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205691-7r06r50","updated":"20230305205691"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用volatile定义的变量，是易改变的，即告诉cpu每次用volatile变量的时候，重新去内存中取保证用的是最新的值,而不是寄存器中的备份。volatile 关键字现在较少适用","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205692-7eo1zr2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205692-7eo1zr2","updated":"20230305205692"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二维数组","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205693-c2i6kk3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205693-c2i6kk3","updated":"20230305205693"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"int a[2][4];","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205694-5m3xeti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205694-5m3xeti","updated":"20230305205694"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解释︰","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义一个名为a的二维数组，每一个元素都是int类型这个二维数组中包含两行四列的元素，一共有8个元素二维数组也是连续开辟空间，访问元素是行和列都是从0开始，分别是a[0][0] a[0][1]a[0][2] a[0][3]a[1][0]a[1][1]a[1][2]a[1][3]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意∶二维数组的下标也是可以省略的，但是有条件，在初始化时行数可以省略，但是列数不能省略"}]},{"ID":"20230305205695-sipmbly","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205695-sipmbly","updated":"20230305205695"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"变量的存储类别","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205696-m6erbg8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205696-m6erbg8","updated":"20230305205696"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"内存的分区:","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205697-4v2wbst","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205697-4v2wbst","updated":"20230305205697"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、内存:物理内存、虚拟内存","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205698-yq25ch4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205698-yq25ch4","updated":"20230305205698"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"物理内存:"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实实在在存在的存储设备虚拟内存:操作系统虚拟出来的内存。操作系统会在物理内存和虚拟内存之间做映射。在32位系统下，每个进程的寻址范围是4G,0x00 00 00 00 ~0xff ff ff ff，在写应用程序的，看到的都是虚拟地址。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205699-hvwvndr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205699-hvwvndr","updated":"20230305205699"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t  在32位操作系统中，虚拟内存被分为两个部分，3G的用户空间和1G内核空间，其中用户空间是当前进程所私有的，内核空间，是一个系统中所有的进程所公有的","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205700-p4tsjgc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205700-p4tsjgc","updated":"20230305205700"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、在运行程序的时候，操作系统会将虚拟内存进行分区","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205701-vnj4qk9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205701-vnj4qk9","updated":"20230305205701"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1).堆在动态申请内存的时候，在堆里开辟内存。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205702-pa0msme","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205702-pa0msme","updated":"20230305205702"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2).栈主要存放局部变量。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205703-6502emn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205703-6502emn","updated":"20230305205703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3).静态全局区1∶未初始化的静态全局区静态变量(定义变量的时候，前面加static修饰）)，或全局变量，没有初始化的，存在此区","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205704-y6q0970","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205704-y6q0970","updated":"20230305205704"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t\t\t2：初始化的静态全局区全局变量、静态变量，赋过初值的，存放在此区","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205705-vizmv7n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205705-vizmv7n","updated":"20230305205705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4).代码区：存放程序代码","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205706-q81xmnl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205706-q81xmnl","updated":"20230305205706"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5).文字常量区","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205707-xavlhwg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205707-xavlhwg","updated":"20230305205707"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"局部变量","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205708-3oicfwg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205708-3oicfwg","updated":"20230305205708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果普通局部变量不进行初始化，则默认是随机值","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205709-la5zb46","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205709-la5zb46","updated":"20230305205709"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果静态局部变量不进行初始化，则默认是0","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205710-k86ev7i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205710-k86ev7i","updated":"20230305205710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态局部变量不会随着当前函数执行结束而释放空间，下次使用的函数之前的空间静态局部变量只会初始化一次","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205711-6n6ezch","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205711-6n6ezch","updated":"20230305205711"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230112193407-t97txls-20230305205815-1oegbaw.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20230305205712-ton1ve7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205712-ton1ve7","updated":"20230305205712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"结果：101 102 103","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205713-3mvgt7y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205713-3mvgt7y","updated":"20230305205713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C语言编译过程","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205714-ejhnkui","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205714-ejhnkui","updated":"20230305205714"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"预处理、编译、汇编、链接","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205715-3iqfxtu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205715-3iqfxtu","updated":"20230305205715"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230112194329-0xqqjy6-20230305205815-bxunzis.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20230305205716-0tul2se","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205716-0tul2se","updated":"20230305205716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1∶预编译","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205717-zn3vi25","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205717-zn3vi25","updated":"20230305205717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将.c中的头文件展开、宏展开，生成的文件是.i文件","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205718-re8ysci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205718-re8ysci","updated":"20230305205718"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2∶编译","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将预处理之后的.i文件生成.s汇编文件","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205719-yq5jwup","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205719-yq5jwup","updated":"20230305205719"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、汇编","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将.s汇编文件生成.o目标文件","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205720-armkb09","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205720-armkb09","updated":"20230305205720"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4、链接","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将.o文件链接成目标文件","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205721-jj3sc3d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205721-jj3sc3d","updated":"20230305205721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"include","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205722-q068e3o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205722-q068e3o","updated":"20230305205722"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230112194508-1d3czm2-20230305205815-17ww94l.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20230305205723-f9fdpkl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205723-f9fdpkl","updated":"20230305205723"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"define","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205724-0pkk1sm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205724-0pkk1sm","updated":"20230305205724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义宏用define去定义，宏是在预编译的时候进行替换。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205725-b5tb4ft","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205725-b5tb4ft","updated":"20230305205725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、不带参宏","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205726-rs41nst","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205726-rs41nst","updated":"20230305205726"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"#define PI 3.14","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205727-1u8lq7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205727-1u8lq7k","updated":"20230305205727"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在预编译的时候如果代码中出现了PI就用3.14去替换。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205728-5n2etx3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205728-5n2etx3","updated":"20230305205728"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宏的好处∶只要修改宏定义，其他地方在预编译的时候就会重新替换。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205729-713bip9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205729-713bip9","updated":"20230305205729"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意:宏定义后边不要加分号。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205730-rnyzv80","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205730-rnyzv80","updated":"20230305205730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、带参宏","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205731-u3uv1t6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205731-u3uv1t6","updated":"20230305205731"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"#define s(a,b) a*b","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205732-zolohuc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205732-zolohuc","updated":"20230305205732"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意带参宏的形参a和b没有类型名，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"S(2,4)将来在预处理的时候替换成实参替代字符串的形参，其他字符保留，2*4","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205733-lm5ubwh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230305205733-lm5ubwh","updated":"20230305205733"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、带参宏和带参函数的区别","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305205734-wv476l0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305205734-wv476l0","updated":"20230305205734"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"带参宏被调用多少次就会展开多少次，执行代码的时候没有函数调用的过程，不需要压栈弹栈。所以带参宏，是浪费了空间，因为被展开多次，节省时间。带参函数，代码只有一份，存在代码段，调用的时候去代码段取指令，调用的时候要压栈弹栈。有个调用的过程。所以说，带参函数是浪费了时间，节省了空间.带参函数的形参是有类型的，带参宏的形参没有类型名。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20230305210055-5uhpxtx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305210055-5uhpxtx","updated":"20230305210651"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选择性编译"}]},{"ID":"20230305211523-1a4xnj5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305211523-1a4xnj5","updated":"20230305211533"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选择性编译是在预编译阶段干的事情"}]},{"ID":"20230305211116-4lwn0pk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305211116-4lwn0pk","updated":"20230305211117"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1."}]},{"ID":"20230305210836-fsr708x","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230305210836-fsr708x","updated":"20230305211059"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#ifdef AAA\n    代码段1\n#else\n    代码段2\n#endif\n\n如果在当前.c ifdef上边定义过AAA，就编译代码段1，否则编译代码段2\n\n注意和if else语句的区别，if else语句都会被编译，通过条件选择性执行代码，而选择性编译只有一块代码被编译\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230305211048-0ozzh08","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20230305211048-0ozzh08","updated":"20230305211135"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230305211135-0j39eb4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20230305211135-0j39eb4","updated":"20230305211135"},"Children":[{"ID":"20230305211135-azodg1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305211135-azodg1f","updated":"20230305211135"}}]}]},{"ID":"20230305211141-ovh69mk","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230305211141-ovh69mk","updated":"20230305211304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#ifndef AAA\n    代码段1\n#else\n    代码段2\n#endif\n\n和第一种互补\n这种方法，经常用在防止头文件重复包含\n常用于多文件编程中的.h的第一行就是#ifndef，最后一行就是#endif\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230305211257-nn08oj6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305211257-nn08oj6","updated":"20230305211354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3."}]},{"ID":"20230305211354-5xtzf8p","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230305211354-5xtzf8p","updated":"20230305211502"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#if 表达式\n    代码段1\n#else\n    代码段2\n#endif\n如果表达式为真，编译第一段代码，否则编译第二段代码\n这种形式一般用于注释多行代码\n\n#if 0\n...\n#endif\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230305211543-jug7n3u","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20230305211543-jug7n3u","updated":"20230305211547"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针"}]},{"ID":"20230310185052-ywnxdt0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230310185052-ywnxdt0","updated":"20230310185100"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针的定义"}]},{"ID":"20230305211548-1wh598j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230305211548-1wh598j","updated":"20230310183641"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操作系统给每个存储单元分配了一个编号， 从0x00000000 ~ 0xffffffff ，这个编号称之为地址"}]},{"ID":"20230310183644-xaejnxz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310183644-xaejnxz","updated":"20230310183952"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230310183751-erby27z.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一共是4G的空间"}]},{"ID":"20230310183946-oci7a6w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310183946-oci7a6w","updated":"20230310184021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针变量：这个变量用来存放一个地址编号"}]},{"ID":"20230310184021-8l4syn2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310184021-8l4syn2","updated":"20230310184103"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在32位平台下，地址总线是32位的，所以地址是32位编号，所以指针变量是32位的即4个字节"}]},{"ID":"20230310184103-vgngvhq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310184103-vgngvhq","updated":"20230310184532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意："},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230310184515-pljdk8y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310184515-pljdk8y"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.无论什么类型的地址，都是存储单元的编号，在32位平台下都是4个字节，即任何类型的指针变量都是4个字节大小"}]},{"ID":"20230310184512-j1yxa65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310184512-j1yxa65","updated":"20230310184619"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.对应类型的指针变量，只能存放对应类型的变量的地址"}]},{"ID":"20230310184619-ydi4z1h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310184619-ydi4z1h","updated":"20230310184925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 75%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230310184919-yln92ay.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 75%;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230310185109-69za0e7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230310185109-69za0e7","updated":"20230310185114"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针的定义方法"}]},{"ID":"20230310185116-67s5mym","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230310185116-67s5mym","updated":"20230310205305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1.简单的指针"}]},{"ID":"20230310194632-4695glq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194632-4695glq","updated":"20230310194649"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t数据类型*  指针变量名；"}]},{"ID":"20230310194649-cwuzduo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194649-cwuzduo","updated":"20230310194716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\tint* p; //定义了一个指针变量p"}]},{"ID":"20230310194716-cbeng0p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194716-cbeng0p","updated":"20230310194740"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t在定义指针变量的时候*是用来修饰变量的，说明变量p是个指针变量"}]},{"ID":"20230310194741-h1av155","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194741-h1av155","updated":"20230311164054"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t变量名是p                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             "}]},{"ID":"20230310194747-84sl6vt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230310194747-84sl6vt","updated":"20230310205306"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2.关于指针的运算符"}]},{"ID":"20230310194803-qtlsj6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194803-qtlsj6a","updated":"20230310194812"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t\u0026取地址、*取值"}]},{"ID":"20230310194812-g8mzpa4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194812-g8mzpa4"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t"}]},{"ID":"20230310194815-tgnl1sc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194815-tgnl1sc","updated":"20230310194824"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t\u0026：获取一个变量的地址"}]},{"ID":"20230310194825-7ez7dd3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194825-7ez7dd3","updated":"20230310194923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t*：在定义一个指针变量时，起到标识作用，标识定义的是一个指针变量，除此之外其他地方都标识获取一个指针变量保存的地址的里面的内容"}]},{"ID":"20230310194924-0netl9w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310194924-0netl9w","updated":"20230310203154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230310203154-zdqto7j.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20230310203238-z9galjb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310203238-z9galjb"}},{"ID":"20230310203239-j43p25u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310203239-j43p25u","updated":"20230310203857"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"扩展：如果在一行中定义多个指针变量，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"每个指针变量前面都需要加*来修饰"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230310203314-n8dxugd","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230310203314-n8dxugd","updated":"20230310203852"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int *p,*q;//定义了两个整型的指针变量p和q\nint* p,q;//定义了一个整型指针变量p，和整形的变量q！！！\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230310203909-jf3ul8m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310203909-jf3ul8m"}},{"ID":"20230310203858-err2qdi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230310203858-err2qdi","updated":"20230310205302"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3、指针大小"}]},{"ID":"20230310205229-65vx9dy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310205229-65vx9dy","updated":"20230310205258"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在64位系统下，所有类型的指针都是4个字节"}]},{"ID":"20230310205330-rqqyabz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310205330-rqqyabz","updated":"20230310205429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为不管地址内的空间多大，但是地址编号的长度都是一样的，所以在64位操作系统中，地址都是8个字节"}]},{"ID":"20230310205258-vpqh90c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310205258-vpqh90c","updated":"20230310205259"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230310205259-dfv3msx.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20230310205308-qc9wjyi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230310205308-qc9wjyi"}},{"ID":"20230310205449-qfw4icw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230310205449-qfw4icw","updated":"20230310205456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"4.指针的分类"}]},{"ID":"20230312092424-ekma7e5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312092424-ekma7e5","updated":"20230312092439"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.字符指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312092439-5rr58dg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312092439-5rr58dg","updated":"20230312092556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"字符型数据的地址\nchar *p;//定义了一个字符指针变量，只能存放字符型数据的地址编号\nchar ch;\np = \u0026ch;\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230310205457-vssnd7x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230310205457-vssnd7x","updated":"20230312092620"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.短整型指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312092622-5ubfmq2","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312092622-5ubfmq2","updated":"20230312092755"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"short *p;//定义了一个短整型的指针变量p，只能存放短整型变量的地址\nshort a;\np = \u0026a;\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312092625-kpmiqif","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312092625-kpmiqif","updated":"20230312092633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.整型指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312092633-5bxxbvp","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312092633-5bxxbvp","updated":"20230312092843"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int *p;\nint a;\np = \u0026a\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312092846-ctnln0a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312092846-ctnln0a","updated":"20230312093006"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注："},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多字节变量，占多个存储单元，每个存储单元都有地址编号，c语言规定，存储单元编号最小的那个编号，是多字节变量的地址编号"}]},{"ID":"20230312092636-ppsddev","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312092636-ppsddev","updated":"20230312092642"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.长整型指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093020-4suufvs","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093020-4suufvs","updated":"20230312093148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"long int *p;\nlong int a;\np = \u0026a\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312093150-bddmmjf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093150-bddmmjf","updated":"20230312093201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.float型的指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093203-r0x3j8w","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093203-r0x3j8w","updated":"20230312093215"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"float *p;\nfloat a;\np = \u0026a\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312093216-tfaavaw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093216-tfaavaw","updated":"20230312093227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.double型指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093231-rnbica1","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093231-rnbica1","updated":"20230312093240"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"double *p;\ndouble a;\np = \u0026a\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312093241-p4xz2rb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093241-p4xz2rb","updated":"20230312093252"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.函数指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093252-zn9bi88","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093252-zn9bi88","updated":"20230312093256"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8.结构体指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093256-fwym6f6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093256-fwym6f6","updated":"20230312093302"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.指针的指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093302-rt1zbzi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093302-rt1zbzi","updated":"20230312093307"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.数组指针"}]},{"ID":"20230312093356-r360xf6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230312093356-r360xf6","updated":"20230312093408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针和变量的关系"}]},{"ID":"20230312093728-fi180ox","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312093728-fi180ox","updated":"20230312093746"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针就是用来存放变量的地址的"}]},{"ID":"20230312093751-i3y66gr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312093751-i3y66gr","updated":"20230312094025"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"*+指针变量 就相当于指针指向的变量  "}]},{"ID":"20230312094025-j9inhi7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312094025-j9inhi7","updated":"20230312094104"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int a;\na = 100;\nint *p;\np = \u0026a;\n*p = 100;\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312093410-duy44q9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312093410-duy44q9","updated":"20230312093707"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针变量只能保存已经开辟好空间的地址，不能随便自己指定地址"}]},{"ID":"20230312095324-mbx3y99","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095324-mbx3y99"}},{"ID":"20230312095626-qzhi3w9","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20230312095626-qzhi3w9","updated":"20230312095724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20230312095631-pk8ovm1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095631-pk8ovm1","updated":"20230312095639"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对应类型的指针只能保存对应类型数据的地址；"}]},{"ID":"20230312095414-1jbo4nx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095414-1jbo4nx","updated":"20230312095433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果想让不同类型的指针相互赋值的时候，需要强制类型转换"}]},{"ID":"20230312095644-5wc1j43","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095644-5wc1j43","updated":"20230312095724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为此处指针类型为字符型指针只能存放一个字节所以需要强转"}]}]},{"ID":"20230312095328-a89j3sh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095328-a89j3sh","updated":"20230312095329"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230312095329-63f0qr6.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20230312095332-87a9tua","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095332-87a9tua","updated":"20230312095807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意："}]},{"ID":"20230312095809-8b08g2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095809-8b08g2l","updated":"20230312095930"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1：*+指针取值，取几个字节由指针类型决定的，指针为字符指针则取一个字节，指针为整型指针则取4个字节，指针为double型指针则取8个字节"}]},{"ID":"20230312095932-w1ltwtx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095932-w1ltwtx","updated":"20230312095955"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2：指针++指向下个对应类型的数据"}]},{"ID":"20230312095955-72x787i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312095955-72x787i","updated":"20230312100023"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t字符指针++，指向下个字符数据，指针存放的地址编号+1"}]},{"ID":"20230312100024-uv2eiu0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312100024-uv2eiu0","updated":"20230312100051"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t整形指针++，指向下个整型数据，指针存放的地址编号+4"}]},{"ID":"20230312100319-aexjo4y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230312100319-aexjo4y","updated":"20230312100332"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针和数组元素之间的关系"}]},{"ID":"20230312100344-o8jwntl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312100344-o8jwntl","updated":"20230312100610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组是多个相同类型的变量的集合"}]},{"ID":"20230312100610-hd8geeh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312100610-hd8geeh","updated":"20230312100627"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每个变量都占内存空间，都有地址编号"}]},{"ID":"20230312100628-bx23cjv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312100628-bx23cjv","updated":"20230312100643"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针变量也可以存放数组元素的地址"}]},{"ID":"20230312100730-yh8r033","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312100730-yh8r033","updated":"20230312100742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（以下两个方法一致）"}]},{"ID":"20230312100643-kijn4ki","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312100643-kijn4ki","updated":"20230312100709"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int a[10];\nint *p = \u0026a[0]\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312100711-d3573kd","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312100711-d3573kd","updated":"20230312100842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int *p;\np = \u0026a[0];//指针变量p保存了数组a中第0个元素的地址，即a[0]的地址\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312101058-j5szzl5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20230312101058-j5szzl5","updated":"20230312101107"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组元素的引用方法"}]},{"ID":"20230312101112-qft2rt6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312101112-qft2rt6","updated":"20230312101406"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//方法一 数组名[下标]\nint a[10];\na[2] = 100;\n\n//方法二\nint a[10];\nint *p;\np = a;\np[2] = 100;//因为p和a等价\n//p和a的不同，p是指针变量，而a是个常量，所以可以用等号给p赋值，但不能给a赋值\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312101153-ylgbdvn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312101153-ylgbdvn","updated":"20230312101410"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注："},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"c语言规定，数组的名字就是数组的首地址，即第0个元素的地址，是个常量"}]},{"ID":"20230312101308-rqatjuo","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312101308-rqatjuo","updated":"20230312101642"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//方法三\nint a[10];\nint *p;\np = a;\n*(p+2)=100;//也是可以的，相当于a[2]=100\n//p是第0个元素的地址，p+2是a[2]这个元素的地址，对第二个元素的地址取值，即a[2]\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312101644-pss2ry6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312101644-pss2ry6","updated":"20230312102042"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 50%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230312102038-kcsiosz.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 50%;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230312102052-rvkrmdj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230312102052-rvkrmdj","updated":"20230312102059"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针的运算"}]},{"ID":"20230312102100-i65hrh5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312102100-i65hrh5","updated":"20230312104445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.指针可以加一个整数，往下指几个它指向的变量，结果还是个地址"}]},{"ID":"20230312104445-cwq2c9v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312104445-cwq2c9v","updated":"20230312104502"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前提：指针指向数组的时候，加一个整数才有意义"}]},{"ID":"20230312104524-jzd5pt5","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312104524-jzd5pt5","updated":"20230312104634"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int a[10];\nint *p;\np = a;\np + 2;//p是a[0]的地址 p+2是\u0026a[a]\n//假如p保存的地址编号是2000的话，p+2代表的地址编号是2008\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312120320-k392xlk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312120320-k392xlk","updated":"20230312204717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.两个相同类型指针可以比较大小"}]},{"ID":"20230312204704-cdqk43s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312204704-cdqk43s","updated":"20230312204920"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只有两个相同类型的指针指向同一个数组的元素的时候，比较大小才有意义 比如a[0]地址和a[1]地址比就是a[0]地址小"}]},{"ID":"20230312204633-z1qni9f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312204633-z1qni9f","updated":"20230312204657"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"指向前面元素的指针 \u0026lt; 指向后面元素的指针"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230312204651-jrn2e0m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312204651-jrn2e0m","updated":"20230312205116"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.两个相同类型指针可以做减法"}]},{"ID":"20230312205135-gtkfik6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312205135-gtkfik6","updated":"20230312205148"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.两个相同类型的指针可以相互赋值"}]},{"ID":"20230312205149-egiixx4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312205149-egiixx4","updated":"20230312205225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t注意：只有相同类型的指针才可以相互赋值（void* 类型除外）"}]},{"ID":"20230312205226-yjbw5dr","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312205226-yjbw5dr","updated":"20230312205406"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int *p;\nint *q;\nint a;\np = \u0026a;//p保存了a的地址，p指向了变量a\nq=p;//用p给q赋值，q也保存了a的地址，指向a\n注意：如果类型不相同的指针想要相互复制，必须进行强制类型转换\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312205538-skn6i96","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230312205538-skn6i96","updated":"20230312205542"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针数组"}]},{"ID":"20230312205543-48rp417","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312205543-48rp417","updated":"20230312205652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.指针和数组的关系"}]},{"ID":"20230312205652-l42clpp","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20230312205652-l42clpp","updated":"20230312205809"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20230312205653-gctig2t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312205653-gctig2t","updated":"20230312205721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"概念：指针数组本身是个数组，是个指针数组，是若干个相同类型的指针变量构成的集合"}]}]},{"ID":"20230312205809-bqb871v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312205809-bqb871v","updated":"20230312205846"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意：一般遇到这样的名词，其本质就是后者，所以指针数组本质就是数组"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230312205608-4ntmu60","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312205608-4ntmu60","updated":"20230312210113"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.定义方法"}]},{"ID":"20230312210113-h2gbw4s","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230312210113-h2gbw4s","updated":"20230312210322"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int *p[10];//定义了一个整形的指针数组p，有10个元素每个元素都是int *类型的变量\nint a;\np[1] = \u0026a;\nint b[10];\np[2] = \u0026b[3];\n//p[2]、*(p+2)是等价的，都是指针数组中的第二个元素\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20230312210234-rpu2cc1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312210234-rpu2cc1","updated":"20230312210503"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3."}]},{"ID":"20230312210504-sjj1jfq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230312210504-sjj1jfq","updated":"20230312210513"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 75%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230312210504-1bw3enn.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 75%;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230312210509-xrz92i0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20230312210509-xrz92i0","updated":"20230313140303"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针的指针——二级指针"}]},{"ID":"20230313140207-e9fo5dv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230313140207-e9fo5dv","updated":"20230313140220"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指针的指针，即指针的地址"}]},{"ID":"20230313140802-omvf8sc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20230313140802-omvf8sc","updated":"20230313140802"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 50%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20230313140750-23vvt1k.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 50%;\"}"}]},{"ID":"20230313140452-vg5gx44","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20230313140452-vg5gx44","updated":"20230313140615"},"